'''Baron Pundar''' was a minor ruler of a [[Pundaria|small barony]] in [[Tethyr]] during the [[Tethyrian Interregnum|Interregnum]]&mdash;although this was contested.
{{Quote|Who dares to name that hedge-robber Pundar of Little Consequence "baron"&mdash;and to prey upon ''my'' people?|Countess [[Zaranda Star]]}}
{{TOC limit|3}}
